B

BlockFilter - Class in com.github.jbapple.libfilter
BlockFilter is a block Bloom filter (from Putze et al.'s "Cache-, Hash- and Space-Efficient Bloom Filters") with some twists: Each block is a split Bloom filter - see Section 2.1 of Broder and Mitzenmacher's "Network Applications of Bloom Filters: A Survey".
BytesNeeded(int, double) - Static method in class com.github.jbapple.libfilter.BlockFilter
Calculates the number of bytes needed to create a filter with the given number of distinct values and false positive probability.
